\c 27
\s Isicelo samadodakazi kaZelofehadi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusondela amadodakazi kaZelofehadi\x + 26.33.\x* indodana kaHeferi indodana kaGileyadi indodana kaMakiri indodana kaManase owensendo zikaManase indodana kaJosefa; njalo la ngamabizo amadodakazi akhe: UMahla, uNowa, loHogila, loMilka, loTiriza.
\v 2 Asesima phambi kukaMozisi, laphambi kukaEleyazare umpristi, laphambi kweziphathamandla, lenhlangano yonke, emnyango wethente lenhlangano, esithi:
\v 3 Ubaba wafela enkangala\x + 14.35; 26.64,65.\x*; kodwa yena wayengekho phakathi kweqembu lalabo ababuthana ukumelana leN\nd kosi\nd*, eqenjini likaKora, kodwa wafa esonweni sakhe\x + 16.49.\x*, wayengelamadodana.
\v 4 Kungani ibizo likababa likhutshwe phakathi kosendo lwakhe ngoba engelandodana? Siphe ilifa phakathi kwabafowabo bakababa\x + Eks. 18.15,19. Levi 24.12. Nani 9.8; 15.34.\x*.
\v 5 UMozisi waseluletha udaba lwawo phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 18.15,19. Levi 24.12; Nani 9.8; 15.34.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 7 Amadodakazi kaZelofehadi akhulume iqiniso; uzawanika lokuwanika isabelo selifa phakathi kwabafowabo bakayise\x + 36.2.\x*; uzadlulisela kuwo ilifa likayise.
\v 8 Njalo uzakhuluma ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli usithi: Uba indoda isifa, ingelandodana, lizadlulisela ilifa layo kundodakazi yayo.
\v 9 Njalo uba ingelandodakazi, lizanika abafowabo ilifa layo.
\v 10 Uba-ke ingelabafowabo, lizanika ilifa layo kubafowabo bakayise.
\v 11 Njalo uba uyise engelabafowabo, lizanika ilifa layo esihlotsheni sayo esiseduze layo sosendo lwayo\x + Levi 18.6.\x*, silidle. Njalo kuzakuba yisimiso sesahlulelo ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi\x + 35.29.\x*.
\s UMozisi ukhetha uJoshuwa ukuba ngumkhokheli
\p
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yenyukela kule intaba yeAbarimi\x + 21.11. 33.44,47. Dute. 32.49; Dute. 3.27.34.1.\x*, ubone ilizwe engilinike abantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 13 Lapho usulibonile, lawe uzabuthelwa ebantwini bakini\x + 20.24.\x*, njengoAroni umnewenu wabuthwa;
\v 14 njengokuba lavukela umlayo wami enkangala yeZini, ekuphikisaneni kwenhlangano\x + 20.12,24.\x*, ukungingcwelisa phambi kwamehlo abo. La ngamanzi eMeriba\x + 20.13. Dute. 32.51. Eks. 17.7.\x* eKadeshi enkangala yeZini.
\p
\v 15 UMozisi wasekhuluma eN\nd kosi\nd*ni esithi:
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wemimoya yenyama yonke, kayimise indoda enhlanganweni\x + 16.22.\x*,
\v 17 engaphuma phambi kwabo, lengangena phambi kwabo, lengabakhokhela baphume, lengabangenisa\x + Dute. 31.2. 1 Sam. 18.13. 1 Kho. 3.7. 2 Lan. 1.10.\x*, ukuze inhlangano yeN\nd kosi\nd* ingabi njengezimvu ezingelamelusi\x + 1 Kho. 22.17. Zek. 10.2. Mat. 9.36. Mark. 6.34.\x*.
\p
\v 18 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Zithathele uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, indoda okukuyo umoya\x + Gen. 41.38. Hlu. 3.10.\x*, ubeke isandla sakho phezu kwayo\x + Dute. 34.9.\x*,
\v 19 uyimise phambi kukaEleyazare umpristi laphambi kwenhlangano yonke, uyilaye phambi kwamehlo abo\x + Dute. 3.28. 31.7,8.\x*,
\v 20 ubusubeka okodumo lwakho phezu kwayo, ukuze inhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli ilalele\x + Josh. 1.16,17.\x*.
\v 21 Njalo izakuma phambi kukaEleyazare umpristi ozayibuzela\x + Josh. 9.14. Hlu. 1.1. 20.18,23,27. 1 Sam. 22.10. 23.2,4. 30.8; 2 Sam. 2.1. 5.19,23,.\x* njengokwesahlulelo sikaUrimi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; ngomlomo wayo bazaphuma, langomlomo wayo bazangena, yona labantwana bonke bakoIsrayeli kanye layo, ngitsho inhlangano yonke.
\v 22 UMozisi wasesenza njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuye. Wathatha uJoshuwa, wammisa phambi kukaEleyazare umpristi laphambi kwenhlangano yonke,
\v 23 wabeka izandla zakhe phezu kwakhe, wamlaya, njengokukhuluma kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi.
